                    "text": "<p>Patent leather might mark fairly easily, but it cleans even easier. All you need is a couple of<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/uk/en_gb/p/ac777000\">cloths</a>, some water, a<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/uk/en_gb/p/AC776000\">shoe brush</a>and a bottle of<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/uk/en_gb/p/ac770001\">Patent Cleaner</a>. It shouldn’t take more than 15 minutes or so.</p>",
